该包提供了 Node.js 的类型定
```
npm i --save-dev @types/node
npm install --save-dev @types/node @types/validator
npm install sequelize reflect-metadata sequelize-typescript
sequelize-typescript@0.5.0
```
### 初始化

1. 安装 VS Code https://code.visualstudio.com/
2. 安装 VS Code 插件 Remote https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ms-vscode-remote.remote-containers
3. 安装 Docker https://www.docker.com/
4. 用 VS Code 打开 `xiangx.code-workspace`
5. 点击左下角绿色按钮，选择 `Remote-Containers: Reopen in Container`
